# Change Log
All notable changes to this package will be documented in this file.

## [2.1]
### Added
#### Device Detection 2.1
- Support for new data file (smaller memory footprint, better third-party browsers coverage).
- Config option to manage internal cache size.
- Config and performance guide (README.DeviceApi-Config.html).
#### Client-side 1.3
 - Battery API detection ("js.battery" property).
 - Capability to extend main class with custom properties.

### Changed
#### Device Detection 2.1
- Any changes to a defined Config object will not affect an existing DeviceApi instance unless the
  set config method of DeviceApi is called.

## [2.0] - 2014-05-13
### Added
- Leveraging the use of all HTTP headers.
- Language detection capability.
- New examples.
- README.Upgrade.html to assist migration from 1.x to 2.0.
